TI  - Data visualization of crime data using immersive virtual reality
PY  - 2022
SN  - 2470-1173
T2  - Electronic Imaging
DO  - 10.2352/ei.2022.34.12.ervr-187
UR  - https://doi.org/10.2352/ei.2022.34.12.ervr-187
